          "Students who had records but did not follow through to the CMBSEwere excluded from the sample. \n\nThe features were extracted from the CES data. Data was normalized and the selection of features was done with the recourse to SHAP. Authors evaluate multple oversampling techniques to address class imbalance (ROS, SMOTE, RUS, Tomek and SMOTE TOMEK), with SMOTE Tomek being selected as the “final” option.",
