          "Authors present a set of models to predict performance on a test. \n\nAuthors do a standard ML pipeline with Feature Selection being done with SHAP. \n\nThe models are evaluated using multiple metrics and the Ensemble methods achieved the best performance.",
          "- Requreiires generalization to other contexts (even within medical education)\n\n- Importance of different courses needs to be adjusted.\n\n- No access to admission records.\n\n- Requires validation in bigger contexts."
