    {
      "id": "9d08a88b-8293-4556-bac5-8cea4bb070cf",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors propose a model whose intention is to predict how well a student will perform in an high-stakes exam. Authors make a comparison between classical ML models and Ensemble-based models.",
