    {
      "id": "f0cea01f-baf6-4dad-a61d-7f18cbb780ef",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Models are assessed on a dataset of medical students collected over a period of 5 years (1005 students). Ensemble models obtain better results at predicting the status on CMBSE exam (Regression Task). Moreover, the GPA on different important disciplines taken throughout the course exhibit high correlations with the outcomes. ",
